title: Danny & Danny Roberts (The Real World: New Orleans)
itunes:title: Danny & Danny Roberts (The Real World: New Orleans)
description:
Danny talks to gay icon Danny Roberts of The Real World New Orleans, who is back on screen on The Real World Homecoming on Paramount+. The two Dannys discuss what it was like coming back to TV, the pressure of representing a community, Dawson's Creek, sexual awakenings, and SO much more!
